Program: Outlook
Title: The detective and the diamond heist: Part 2
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswt78
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 11 Mar 2019
In 2003, a band of expert criminals had masterminded the biggest and boldest jewel robbery in history, but Belgian diamond detective Patrick Peys was on their trail. A strange assortment of clues, including a carpet and a salami sandwich, led to a mysterious criminal mastermind and a school for felons. Presenter: Emily Webb Producer: Maryam Maruf Image: Patrick Peys Credit: Emily Webb Show less